    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_52_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "初めて泣いた映画か\n舞台を訪れてこれだけ感動するのも納得だな",
      "startTime": 140.9999928365,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_52_02-ngs012.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんです。今はもう、この場所の空気を\n吸うだけでも十分幸せで……あ",
      "startTime": 148.9333343078,
      "sfxList": []
