      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_52_02-ngs016.m4a",
      "text": "聖地にやって来て、しかも映画さながらのカップルを\n見かけるなんて凄い偶然……わわわ！？",
      "startTime": 192.6333261699,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
